{"tid":260990,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[劣根性] 覺唔覺星期6、日搞結婚/請飲係蝗底仆街","createTime":"2017-05-28T05:52:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-28T07:13:23.000Z","uid":7854,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"24a9ba6d5c59f36c9865676ce14be23fafc368cf","tid":260990,"uid":7854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T05:52:37.000Z","msg":"屌你老母放假日子先黎搞埋d咁既野<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n難得放假 仲要人曬時間曬錢黎睇你場大龍鳳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80897c916b7e045482b8541c43d7311c217cbba7","tid":260990,"uid":7854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T05:54:21.000Z","msg":"播埋d片段講真無人想知<br />\n<br />\n淨係想拿拿林食完餐蝕錢飯就走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"557f4c64aa5758b96559f0648fe417a47e48a7ba","tid":260990,"uid":98692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T05:55:17.000Z","msg":"你禮到就得，人唔到無人care<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24144488aea456087953deb150b63c196c898926","tid":260990,"uid":73269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T05:56:44.000Z","msg":"你地都唔真心祝福人, 咪去羅"},{"pid":"292b5b785ca21415c834520fe23d148c88abf79b","tid":260990,"uid":104941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T06:00:16.000Z","msg":"最好係星期五搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56d6f11531296dbaff91ad2701d5ffe83327c55d","tid":260990,"uid":7854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T06:00:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你禮到就得，人唔到無人care<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔去咪蝕得仲甘 根本被請飲已經係必輸局面<br />\n<br />\n根本係出錢請人結婚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99ceada0ef2311def13663c698d5b2313838a2f7","tid":260990,"uid":98692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T06:24:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你禮到就得，人唔到無人care<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔去咪蝕得仲甘 根本被請飲已經係必輸局面<br />\n<br />\n根本係出錢請人結婚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />就是想你出錢先比帖你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"641d3ff57f40226092bf49551d9541608b053f3c","tid":260990,"uid":63154,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T06:30:35.000Z","msg":"根本就唔應該再搞擺酒，浪費金錢，啲賓客其實內心又唔係咁想黎，最好借樓價貴過橋，話儲錢買樓唔擇酒"},{"pid":"be2678447607c45dc2032de4e560c9edf3748084","tid":260990,"uid":4213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T07:13:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>根本就唔應該再搞擺酒，浪費金錢，啲賓客其實內心又唔係咁想黎，最好借樓價貴過橋，話儲錢買樓唔擇酒</blockquote><br />\n每次見到你啲蠢人就想笑<br />\n咩柒唔好擺酒<br />\n個問題係出係擺酒嘅心態 而唔係擺酒嘅行為<br />\n有一班低能擺酒要搞大佢 但又請啲唔熟嘅人<br />\n搞到大家受苦 呢個問題出現係因為擺酒嘅人On9<br />\n同時都有大把人擺酒係為左分享喜悅<br />\n賺蝕根本唔在意<br />\n只係因為你呢啲低下階層接觸開啲低下人種<br />\n所以擺親酒都好似要你受罪咁姐<br />\n用下個腦啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}